{"tid":1718242,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"陳奕迅-六月飛霜","createTime":"2019-11-13T20:25:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T21:57:15.000Z","uid":250869,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c3bbb6fecc00299487ec66753e1bd412f8f278bc","tid":1718242,"uid":250869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T20:25:34.000Z","msg":"我正式宣佈這是反映2019年香港社會現況的重要歌曲之一。<br />\n<br />\n聽到喊撚左出黎<br />\n<br />\n每句歌詞配合什麼社會狀況，靠大家腦補。<br />\n<br />\n「最終 習慣為著獵取一身盔甲竟不怕損傷<br />\n為了夢幻日子得到保障 用惡夢結賬」<br />\n<br />\n「埋下理想栽種幻想」<br />\n<br />\n「欲求未滿 剩下砒霜 當菜汁分享<br />\n猶如吞仙丹上月亮 誰有膽設想這世間下場」<br />\n<br />\n「即使你跟我比鬥已極平常」<br />\n<br />\n「習慣了這異象 誰又在叫嚷」<br />\n<br />\n「人人一把口一百種真相 誰說得漂亮」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KlIoLizlF3s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKlIoLizlF3s&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZAUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=b7d41e99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KlIoLizlF3s</a>"},{"pid":"c6df636b5a2efcb3884c0012c0127706f25d659b","tid":1718242,"uid":316839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T21:57:15.000Z","msg":"邊個叫我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}